(34, 4, '江理“十佳校媒之星”，他们是谁？', '江西理工大学党宣新媒体中心', '2016-12-22 19:42:37', '江西理工大学微信公众号', '<section><section><section><section><section><section><p style="margin: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; border-color: rgb(245, 245, 244); white-space: normal;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(149, 55, 52); line-height: 21px; text-indent: 28px;">2016年到了，校媒大家庭也携手走过了七个年头，在这七年里，很多校媒人都付出了他们的努力和汗水，他们的成绩我们看得到，他们的付出，我们更看得到！因此，在校媒年会举办之际，校党委宣传部将表彰在2015年度表现突出的校媒人，并评选出“十佳校媒之星”和“优秀校媒人”！快来看看你到底中意谁吧~</span></p></section><section></section></section></section></section><section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section><p><section><section><section><section><span class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">评选背景</span></section></section><section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(61, 61, 61); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;">为充分利用学校传媒资源，加强各宣传部门彼此间的交流合作，弘扬当代大学生积极进取、不断开拓的精神面貌，并对2015年度学校表现突出的校媒人进行肯定和表彰。</span></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><span class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">评选目的</span></section></section><section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(61, 61, 61); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;">1、发挥校园记者的能动作用，及时准确地报道校园新闻。反映最新校园动态，加强校园文化的宣传；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(61, 61, 61); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;">2、表彰一批在2015年度工作中表现突出的校媒人，充分调动校媒人的积极性，展现他们的个性和时代的风采；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 5px 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(61, 61, 61); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;">3、培养校媒人的集体责任感，使命感及荣誉感。热爱校园，服务校园，打造品牌校园文化；</span></p></section></section><section></section></section></p><p class="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; border: 0px none; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p class="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-h