lass="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(2, 2, 2);"><section>看过学长学姐们精心打扮的床铺的样子，有没有觉得很有把自己宿舍好好打扮一番的冲动！南昌校区某几栋是上床下桌，鲜肉们可以自行脑补一下</section></h2></blockquote><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p><section><section><p style="text-align:center"><img class="" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/qTPPIKRc7QqDtgftG45gzXwEu63MRz658At8l9Cowib5U1FNA8px8BibzL9uu9Oe0QMFocsbE38HgNiat3PKhFfPw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1"/></p></section><section><section><section>快递在这</section></section><section><section>就在1栋宿舍楼下</section></section></section><section></section></section></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><blockquote class="" style="margin: 0.5em 0px 0.3em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; border: none; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: inherit; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size: 1.5em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;"><h2 class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(2, 2, 2);"><section>西区校园里基本上涵盖了各大快递代收点，同时也可以寄出，方便的很！</section></h2></blockquote><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p><section><section><section><p style="text-align:center"><img class="" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/qTPPIKRc7QqDtgftG45gzXwEu63MRz65icDvPgKHmXk0licrPNZypDKCFxvItCcBOLicuD8qFM2w265W3oic5GGp7g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1"/></p><section></section></section></section><section><section>—洗衣房</section></section><section><section>有些手洗有难度的衣服、床上用品可以送到洗衣房洗哦，有善良的卖水哥，四块钱一次。</section></section><section></section></section><section><section><section><section></section><section><section></section><section></section></section><section></section><section></section></section><section><section>还有一些技能</section></section></section><section></section></section><section><section><section><section><section>充电费</section></section></section></section><section><section>每一栋宿舍楼都有宿管阿姨（大爷也是有的），宿舍的电费需要及时缴纳哦，否则会在你很畅快的吹着空调或是认真学习的时候停电哦。</section></section><section></section></section><section><section><section><section><section>要买水</section></section></section></section><section><section>宿舍有饮水机，大一时饮水机是赠送的，水需要自己购买，每天放学时宿舍楼下有专门送水的同学为你送货上门，女生7块钱一桶，男生木有暖男送上门，6块钱一桶，需要自己扛回宿舍。ps：送水很辛苦，说声谢谢哦。</section></section><section></section></section><section><section><section><section><section>充水卡</section></section></section></section><section><section>二栋楼下有充热水卡的地方，需要洗热水澡的童鞋可以开学初存上足够的水费，遗憾的事一卡通如果丢失，水卡上的水费是补不回来的噢，为了好好用完你的水费，尽量不要粗心丢掉自己的一卡通哦！</section></section><section></section></section><section><img class="" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/qTPPIKRc7QqDtgftG45gzXwEu63MRz656vOicmEvSMqbew0An4TM99ykl7WrRLIv5Yf1jgPrDGyyqu8chZ77jaQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1"/><section></section></section><section><section><section><span class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0.3em 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; border-radius: 0px 0.5em 0.5em 0px; font-size: 1em; font-family: inherit; background-color: rgb(123, 185, 229);"><section>所以说</section></span><section></section></section><section><section>宿舍生活还是很美好的，尤其是已经装好空调的西校区鲜肉们，好好享受泥萌的大一生活吧！</section></section><section></section><section><section>怀挺！</section></section></section><section></section></section><section><section><section><section></section><section><section></section><section></section></section><section></section><section></section></section><section><section>以及一些制度（严肃脸）</section></section></section><section></section></section><section><section><section><section>大功率</section></section></section><section><span class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; float: left; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.2; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(249, 110, 87);"><section><br/></section></span><span class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.2; font-family: inherit;"><section>宿舍最怕大功率，所以还是不要想偷运一只小锅到宿舍开小灶，结果只能是－－断电。在拔掉饮水机这个算得上是大功率的插头后，可以任性的用小功率吹风机吹一吹女孩子的秀发，打开自己的小风扇凉爽凉爽。</section></span></section><section></section></section><section><section><section><section>有门禁</section></section></section><section><span class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; float: left; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.2; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(249, 110, 87);"><section><br/></section></span><span class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.2; font-family: inherit;"><section>西校区晚上十一点以后算晚归，宿管阿姨会用大铁链锁上门哦，到时候想进门就要用力嘶吼叫醒宿管，到时候还得登记专业班级姓名，运气不好还得被辅导员叫去一顿批，所以同学们记得按时回寝室哦！</section></span></section><section></section></section><section><section><section><section></section><section><section></section><section></section></section><section></section><section></section></section><section><section>还有一些设施</section></section></section><section></section></section><section><section><section><section>1.床宽约0.90m，长1.90m，要是想自己买凉席带去学校，尺寸仅供参考。</section><section>2.上下铺床板间1米左右，上铺距天花板1.5米左右，下铺床板距地板半米不到，不要带太大的箱子哦~除了柜子上面和床底是没有地方放的哦。</section><section>3.空调，毕竟现在是西区的鲜肉们专属，有待你们自己去发掘“美好”的东西吧。</section><section>4.关于晒衣服，统一是在室内晾晒，有足够的地方让你去洗衣服刷鞋子，冬天也可以拿到楼顶天台去晒晒太阳哦。</section></section></section><section></section></section><section><section><section></section><section><span class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0.2em 0.3em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; float: left; font-family: inherit;"><section>最后是神器</section></span></section><section></section></section><section></section></section><section><section><section><section></section><section></section><section></section></section><section><section>各种宿舍神奇在寝室还是能发挥很强大的作用的，下面由小编向你慢慢道来～</section></section><section><section></section><section></section></section></section><section></section></section><section><img class="" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/qTPPIKRc7QqDtgftG45gzXwEu63MRz651AyAcYIbe6qNDDmD0KjxAWXspX2ROuaYj6u6assXwa7yoZqia2DZXUQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1"/><section></section></section><section><section><section>插线板</section><section>这种居家必备的东西想必技能就不需要小编说了，大家都懂得，功能强大。</section></section><section></section></section><section><img class="" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/qTPPIKRc7QqDtgftG45gzXwEu63MRz658uVqyPXltknyYHEOibjwDJReXTYw46MWRhZXnw7DJuiaJYfUlktibSicZA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1"/><section></section></section><section><section><section>楼梯垫</section><section>某宝上种类众多，总有一款适合你。</section></section><section></section></section><section><img class="" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/qTPPIKRc7QqDtgftG45gzXwEu63MRz65Ep7PRRicGh7ddvLiaInnpAM76tYXxJjMj7OAonC3FoFBiaTLIt85f5Nqg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1"/><section></section></section><section><section><section>置物架</section><section>上铺的福音，水杯、手机、纸巾啦什么的都可以放，小编亲身体验推荐上铺的孩纸入一款。</section></section><section></section></section><section><img class="" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/qTPPIKRc7QqDtgftG45gzXwEu63MRz657NzZKYZalPaTqkII4EH1qpsibJghffHG9d8PV5M0LFNcZGicDW2Q2fBQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1"/><section></section></section><section><section><section>小桌子</section><section>高三过来的都懂，小桌子的功能也是多到任你想象。</section></section><section></section></section><section><section><section><section>一点点话</section></section><section></section><section></section></section><section></section></section><section><img class="" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/qTPPIKRc7QqDtgftG45gzXwEu63MRz65MR2mdTdof8I0icxY6Zm14CjHZqchh9A6IKJx2ADgqAHYvyx3RdgHpnw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1"/><section></section></section><section><section><section></section></section><section><section><section></section></section><section><section></section><section><section><section></section><section><section>天下之大，皆为一个缘字也～寝室关系的处理在大学还是很必要的，俗话说一屋不扫何以扫天下，同理，一屋不平何以平天下？一定要和室友们维持着良好的关系哦！</section></section></section></section></section></section></section></p><p><br/></p>');
