-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; text-decoration: inherit; line-height: 1.4; font-weight: inherit;">“烦事未了何以了，难以不了了之。”世人最后却死于追逐的宝藏当中。金钱对于充满贪婪和欲望的人是人性毒药。人性早已被毒药侵蚀，留下的躯壳也终究会糜烂至死。连城诀找到了，宝藏也找到了，可是自己和至亲却找不到了。&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">“素心”才是价值连城的财富，当一切都显得有价的时候，唯有此物才是无价之宝。素心即连城，真情即连城。</span></p></section></section><section></section></section></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; widows: 1; line-height: 17.6552px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p><section><section><section><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px 23px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-color: rgb(194, 201, 42); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; background-color: rgb(194, 201, 42);">我 • 书</span></section><section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px;">测绘152 刘志强</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; font-family: inherit; line-height: 1.4; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; font-family: inherit; line-height: 1.4; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">见不着陌路的繁花，见不着南天的星座，见不着凝霜的枯藤或是流金的宫殿，我的青春是被无数大小琐事所淹没的岛屿，而你便是我心灵停泊的港湾。</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/qTPPIKRc7QqHwj5Nia4kJp0uhOWGzvkDFElypoOvm4ibWxUoTJmvXAmyKK1wP256YuEz6Aql2ENA6vXXyibGiastIA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1"/><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px;">一纸素笺，心事了然，道不尽的无奈，不知文字醉倒了多少痴爱。我与书的关系，绝不是谁牵绊谁。我离不开它，是贪恋那种心弦被触碰的感觉。</span></p></section></section><section></section></section></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; widows: 1; line-height: 17.6552px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p><section><section><section><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px 23px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-color: rgb(194, 201, 42); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; background-color: rgb(194, 201, 42);">书的邂逅</span></section><section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px;">电科151 张国英</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px;">阳光不错。是的，当那一束阳光斜斜地照在图书馆略微泛黄的书桌上时，她不由得抬起了头。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px;">如此良辰，怎可轻负韶华。她看了看堆砌在书桌上的作业，轻轻地叹了一口气，继续埋头于数理化的怀抱。可是阳光挑逗一般，抚摸着她的脸颊，用那灼热的温度强迫她停下了笔。</span></p></section></section><section></section></section></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; widows: 1; line-height: 17.6552px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p><section><section><section><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 8px 23px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-color: rgb(194, 201, 42); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; background-color: rgb(194, 201, 42);">最美的际遇</span></section><section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px;">矿加152 童格</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px;">一池碧水，一榭春花，一场际遇，阅读与我，我与阅读。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: right; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px;">——题记</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px;">头顶一抹明媚，手持一杯香茗，在这浮尘的悠闲里，在这一缕氤氲的茶香下，邂逅一段暖心的文字，就如同在最美好的年华里，邂逅一个人，眼波流转，微笑蔓延，黯然心动。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px;">因为阅读，我们相遇文字，感受自身；因为阅读，我们相识文字，感受生活；因为阅读，我们相拥文字，感受心灵。如果说语言让人类有别于其他动物，那么书籍，便是那让人类超脱于其他动物的物件。</span></p></section></section><section></section></section></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p><section><section><section><br/></section></section></sec